t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[22: Gaagffii cimaa gaafadhu, garuu kabajaan ta'uu akka qabu yaadadhu. Gaaffiin kabajaan gaafatamu bakka fagoo ga'uu danda'a.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[23: Kabaja kennuun  amantaa uumuu fi gaafannoo fooyyessuuf si gargaaruu danda'a.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[14: Yeroon daanga'aa yoo ta'eyyuu, karoora qopheeffadhu, waan argite hunda hin waraabin.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[2]: Yeroo danda'ametti gaaffiif deebiin dura qorannoo tokko tokko geggeessi. Gaaffii caaluu fi baayyee barbaachisaa ta'e gaafadhu.
t_audio_library::title: Seenaa Sagalee Qopheessi
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[3]: Qaamichaaf ibsa seenaake hima tokkoon qabaadhu.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[15: Yeroo gaaffiif deebii waraabdutti, yoo xiqqaate gaaffilee 15 qopheeffadhu.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[5]: Gaaffiiwwankeef caalmaa kennuudhaan tokko kan odeeffannoo barbaachisaa kan ati barbaaddu adda baasi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[28: Odeeffannoo baayyee yoo barbaadde gaaffii hordoffii qabu fayyadami.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[0]: Ofiikee beeki, ilaalchi dogoggoraakee akka seenaakeerratti dhiibbaa hin fidne eeggadhu.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[1]: Yeroo haala sodaachisaa keessatti waraabdutti mala ba'umsaa yeroo hunda qabaadhu.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[33: Muraa hundaaf of gaafadhu: waan haaraa natti himu qabaa?
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[32: Dubbiin ijoo deebii gaaffii kan nama dhaggeeffatu akka dhaggeeffatu godhuudha. Daftee deebistee hin xumurin.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[12: Hamma dandeesse sagaleekee xinneessii fayyadami, seenaakee karaa sagalee namootaa himi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[34: Walitti fufiinsi gaariin suuraalee gaggaarii shan irraa qophaa'uu qaba. Fakkii gaggaarii baayyee yoo qabaatte, itti dabali.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[13: Yeroo mataduree fi dhangii fayyadamtu filattutti waa'ee hordoftoota bira ga'uu barbaadduu yaadi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[16: Seenaa gaarii fi qulqullina qabu himuuf mataduree hangafaa tokkorratti xiyyeeffadhu.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[29: Yaadadhu, sagalee malee fakkiinkee walakkaa seenichaa qofa hima.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[31: Seenaan hundi gaaffii ijoo qaba. Xumurasaa irratti gaaffiin ati deebiste maali?
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[30: Yoo qilleensa'aa jiraate, kaameeraakee qilleensarraa achi qabi, yookaan maayikiikee eegi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[24: Waraabduurratti cuqaasuukeen dura sagalee duubaa jeequudhaan qulqullina seenaakee miidhuu danda'u dhaggeeffadhu.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[10: Gaaffii gaafachuukeen dura utuu dubbachuu hin jalqabin sekoondota yartuuf callisa waraabi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[8]: Yoo gaaffiif deebii namoota qabxii ilaalchaa garagaraa qabanii itti dabalte seenaankee baayyee gaarii ta'a.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[25: Gaaffilee 'cufaa' ta'an kan deebii tokko qofa qaban kan akka 'eeyyee' yookaan 'lakki' jedhu hin gaafatin.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[17: Yeroo danda'ametti jalqabarratti waan argitee fi gaaffiif deebii waraabi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[20: Yeroo hunda gaaffif deebiirraa waan barbaaddu beeki.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[21: Si'a tokkotti gaaffii tokko qofa gaafadhu.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[6]: Saffisaan gara gaaffii barbaachisaa gaaffiif deebii dhaqi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[11: Waraabuu jalqabuukeen dura dhageessistuu gurraa fayyadamuudhaan sadarkaa sagalee ilaali.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[26: Itti fufiinsa haasichaa eegi. Gaafadhu: Maaliif? Itti aanee maaltu ta'e? Maal jechuu keeti?
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[27: Gaaffiinkee deebii barbaachisaa argamsiisuu yoo dadhabe, karaa gaaffiikee jijjiiri.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[19: Tasgabbaa'i, Tasgabbaa'uunkee akka namni wajjin gaaffiif deebii geggeessitu tasgabbaa'uuf gargaara.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[18: Yeroo gaafannoo geggeessuuf gaafattutti waa'ee matadureekee yookaan galmakee ifa godhi.
t_audio_library::text_card_0::text: Seenaa sagalee gaarii qopheessuun muraalee garagaraa hirmaachisa. Qajoojiin kun seenaawwan garagaraa himuuf muraalee barbaaddu akka argattuuf si qajeelcha.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[9]: Duraa duuba gaarii uumuuf waraabbii hammamtaa garagaraa qaban waraabi.
t_audio_library::tip_collection::tips[7]: Gaafannookee keessatti, abshaala garuu gaarii ta'uu yaadadhu.
